<!doctype html>
<html lang="vi" class="h-full">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Không tìm thấy trang | <%= name %></title>
  <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
  <script>
    tailwind.config = {
      theme: {
        extend: {
          fontFamily: {
            sans: ['IBM Plex Sans', 'sans-serif'],
          },
          animation: {
            'float': 'float 4s ease-in-out infinite',
            'pulse-slow': 'pulse 4s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.6, 1) infinite',
          },
          keyframes: {
            float: {
              '0%, 100%': { transform: 'translateY(0) scale(1)' },
              '50%': { transform: 'translateY(-20px) scale(1.05)' },
            }
          }
        }
      }
    }
  </script>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=IBM+Plex+Sans:wght@300;400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  
  <style>
    .gold-gradient {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #BF953F, #FCF6BA, #B38728, #FBF5B7, #AA771C);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    }
    .gold-bg {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #BF953F, #FCF6BA, #B38728, #FBF5B7, #AA771C);
    }
    .gold-shadow {
      box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(179, 135, 40, 0.2);
    }
    .gold-border {
      border: 1px solid rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.3);
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body class="h-full bg-[#050505] text-gray-300 font-sans overflow-hidden">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 overflow-hidden pointer-events-none">
    <div class="absolute top-[-10%] left-[-10%] w-[40%] h-[40%] bg-[#B38728] opacity-5 blur-[120px] rounded-full"></div>
    <div class="absolute bottom-[-10%] right-[-10%] w-[40%] h-[40%] bg-[#B38728] opacity-5 blur-[120px] rounded-full"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center min-h-screen px-4 py-12 relative z-10">
    <div class="w-full max-w-md space-y-12 text-center">
      
      <div class="relative group">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[#B38728] blur-[60px] opacity-10 group-hover:opacity-20 transition-opacity duration-1000"></div>
        <svg class="w-56 h-56 mx-auto animate-float text-[#D4AF37] opacity-80" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1" d="M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1" d="M9 10h.01M15 10h.01M9.172 16.172a4 4 0 015.656 0" />
        </svg>
        <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center">
          <span class="text-7xl font-black tracking-tighter text-white drop-shadow-[0_5px_15px_rgba(0,0,0,0.5)]">404</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div class="inline-block px-3 py-1 rounded-full border gold-border bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-sm">
            <span class="text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.3em] gold-gradient">Lỗi truy cập</span>
        </div>
        
        <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white sm:text-4xl uppercase">
            Bạn đang <span class="gold-gradient">lạc đường?</span>
        </h1>
        
        <p class="text-gray-400 max-w-xs mx-auto text-sm leading-relaxed">
          Trang bạn đang tìm kiếm không tồn tại hoặc đã được chuyển sang một địa chỉ khác trong hệ thống.
        </p>
        
        <div class="pt-8 flex flex-col gap-4 items-center">
          <a href="../" class="gold-bg text-black font-bold px-10 py-4 rounded-full hover:scale-105 active:scale-95 transition-all duration-300 shadow-lg gold-shadow uppercase tracking-widest text-xs flex items-center gap-2">
            <i class="fas fa-arrow-left"></i> Quay lại trang chủ
          </a>
          
          <a href="#" class="text-xs font-semibold text-gray-500 hover:text-[#D4AF37] transition-colors tracking-widest uppercase">
            Liên hệ hỗ trợ kĩ thuật
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="pt-12">
        <p class="text-[10px] text-gray-700 uppercase tracking-[0.5em]">
          Powered by <%= name %> Security
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css">
</body>
</html>